::Prowl::

The roar of engines announces the shuttle's arrival, Prowl watching 
it land several seconds later, a few feet behind him.

"Ok, our ride's here," he says, putting away his staff and picking up 
Firedrill. "Lets get you repaired."

Prowl carries Firedrill into the shuttle and then comes back for the 
other two, putting them all in.

"I'll see you back at base," he says as the hatch closes, the shuttle 
launching off. Prowl lifts into the air, following behind the shuttle.
